        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/dbc845/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2020-05-17T01:56:39.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Bongran was a longtime favorite of mine, used to buy it when we wd visit my wife\u2019s family downstate(Westchester, NY)\u2026Haven\u2019t seen Bongran on the shelves up here in CNY (Syracuse area) and we don\u2019t get downstate that much anymore \u2026Will look for some when  COVID goes away and we can visit family in Westchester or our oldest daughter who lives in NYC.</p>",
